Interface Keyed<KeyType>

  • Type Parameters:
    KeyType - The data type of the key value
    All Superinterfaces:
    Matchable<KeyType>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdvanceTicket, Client, Customer, RegularTicket, StudentAdvanceTicket, Ticket

    public interface Keyed<KeyType>
extends Matchable<KeyType>
    An interface that allows an object to be checked to see if a key value matches the object's key value
    Author:
    Joshua Zierman [py1422xs@metrostate.edu]
